                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840421-44-defend634 t17840421-44-punish259"></join>
               confined to hard labour twelve months in the house of correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron EYRE.</p>
